Just a simple class to determine if another process has already locked a file on a unix filesystem.

Example:

IRB 1>>
p = ProcessLock.new('example.tmp')
p.owner?
=> false
p.aquire!
=> true
p.owner?
=> true

IRB 2>>
q = ProcessLock.new('example.tmp')
p.owner?
=> false
p.aquire!
=> false
p.owner?
=> false
p.alive?
=> true

